<p><strong>6</strong></p>
<p><strong>课程大纲 </strong></p>
<p>Unit 1: 1450 – 1648</p>
<p>Sub-Unit 1A: The Renaissance and Voyages of Discovery</p>
<p>Sub-Unit 1B: Reformation</p>
<p>Sub-Unit 1C: Religious Wars</p>
<p>Unit 2: 1648 – 1815</p>
<p>Sub-Unit 2A: Absolutism and New Thinking</p>
<p>Sub-Unit 2B: The Scientific Revolution and the Enlightenment</p>
<p>Sub-Unit 2C: Eighteenth Century Society and Economy</p>
<p>Sub-Unit 2D: War, Trade, and Rebellion</p>
<p>Sub-Unit 2E: The French Revolution, the Age of Napoleon, and Romanticism</p>
<p>Unit 3: 1815 – 1914</p>
<p>Sub-Unit 3A: The Industrial Revolution and Its Consequences</p>
<p>Sub-Unit 3B: The Age of Nation States</p>
<p>Sub-Unit 3C: The Rise of Europe and Modern Thought</p>
<p>Sub-Unit 3D: The Age of Western Imperialism</p>
<p>Unit 4: 1914 – Present</p>
<p>Sub-Unit A: The Great War and Its Origins</p>
<p>Sub-Unit B: The Interwar Years</p>
<p>Sub-Unit C: World War II</p>
<p>Sub-Unit D: The Cold War Era</p>
<p>Sub-Unit E: Post Cold War World</p>
